fields.title: kernel ridge regression
fields.pointers:
*  [Gaussian process regression](gaussian_process_regression)  is a Bayesian version of kernel ridge regression.
*  [Kernel support vector machines](kernel_svm)  are a classification algorithm that uses kernels.
* Unfortunately, the  [running time of ridge regression](computational_complexity_of_kernel_methods)  is cubic in the number of training examples.
